## Data access
- [STAC catalog root]({{ metadata.url }}stac/): entry point to all dataset STAC Collections — https://stac.dynamical.org/catalog.json
- [Catalog index]({{ metadata.url }}catalog/): human-readable catalog of all datasets
- Datasets are distributed as Icechunk (Zarr) repositories on S3; see the access example and `distribution` in each dataset's JSON-LD or STAC Collection.

## Docs & examples
- Each catalog page includes runnable Python examples and links to example notebooks (GitHub + Colab).
- [Observation data notes]({{ metadata.url }}observation-data/): background on observation datasets.

## Quality & operations
- [Weather station scorecard]({{ metadata.url }}scorecard/): forecast accuracy vs. observations across US weather stations.
- [Status](https://status.dynamical.org): live uptime and incident history.
- Per-dataset validation reports are linked from each catalog page.

